Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:32.68,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,540)}{\fad(1000,380)}奈纱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙琉妮大人 芙琉妮大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙琉妮大人您去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.23,0:01:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭司长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说“去哪了”这种荒谬的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子哪都去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界的万物是相连的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回来了就得好好教训她一下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然偷走了“世界之匙”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.93,0:02:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我忘了打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向新的一天说早上好吧克雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是分身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也未免太逼真了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要摸摸头？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气 请摸一摸头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有触感..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:02:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 很不可思议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱也不太懂自己是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱很不可思议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你是芙琉妮的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙琉妮？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不认识吗 是把你留在这的女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把奈纱留了下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫芙琉妮的人是不是讨厌奈纱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该不是那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱讨厌“讨厌”这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱喜欢“喜欢”这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恰啦恰~恰啦恰~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要给白昼之星许愿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我希望能和克雷恩做很要好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是芙琉妮..的分身吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点飘飘然的奇特女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 说到奇特芙琉妮也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷恩 又带别的女孩来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 这个是昨天那女孩忘记拿走的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记拿走的东西？那是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能碰到分身？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的 这孩子不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不说了吗 是她忘记拿走的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就得还给那个女孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到的话就交给警察吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遗失物吧 那就该…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 好大的发带啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要还 但也不知道芙琉妮在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鸟耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱喜欢鸟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙琉妮也喜欢鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙琉妮…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到了想做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先对她发发火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骂她一顿！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风吹得好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹在脸颊上 一阵阵地吹过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了 会摔下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 摔着了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过反正是分身 没事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸到了 摸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸到了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 感觉有点无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好安静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的什么都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近只有设施而已 警察局啦 办事处之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然留着很多建筑 不过没多少人住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱 你跟着我也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话就在这分…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的钟耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不能随便进去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啊 奈纱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多车子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是来玩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那些机动车就是家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用被任何东西束缚 好像很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使星星坠落 也能轻松离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是飞艇啦 而且村子周围电波也比较稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有家什么的 不是更轻松吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 克雷恩有家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘛 是因为喜欢旧的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然经常被妈妈发牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都迷路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没有可以说“我回来了”的家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有了家 就算说声“我回来了”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着的也只有分身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一开始就没有任何束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 我觉得也就不用特地再被一个家束缚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了吧 适可而止吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你在看什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 那个是比被别人摸摸头更令人高兴的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在这里睡觉的啊 厕所在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱 我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊 克雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宝宝很高兴呢 都笑出酒窝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 奈纱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞了飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:09:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那家伙才变得乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我赔偿啊 你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被别人弄得这么团团转的还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好开心啊 克雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 接下来要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去把你托给他们 不能继续在一块了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 奈纱要和克雷恩在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是奈纱的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是克雷恩叫奈纱出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以克雷恩在的地方就是奈纱的家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 奈纱的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:10:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷恩 变得碰不到奈纱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去警察局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你说她是遗失物… 总之先让她呆在这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 克雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 偷走了我们的零件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是回礼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回..礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:11:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们三个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您带来了 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼 搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 就是你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个巫女藏起来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位少年 那个女人在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了早上就不知跑哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！色狼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一起待到早上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是个大色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yes sir
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张口闭口都是少年..你不也是个少年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在野营地发生的骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你引起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我啦 是芙琉妮的分身..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在她身在何处我可就不清楚了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道跑哪里去了 自说自话就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 你明明就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是大色狼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这样那样的事一定都清楚得很啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色狼色狼地烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我根本就不是色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是工作还是干活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有麻烦事分身都会帮你做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以自己的发肤所直接感受到的东西..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种冲击根本无法比拟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的没错吧 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不说我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么“你可以回去了”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全地被跟踪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们真以为自己没有被发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正芙琉妮和奈纱也都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个房子 原来就这么大间吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有自己的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就不怎么喜欢 世上存在另一个我的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以实在不爽被那家伙说三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸得到的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 已经有在开发了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱果然是..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让用来编绘分身的电脑计算出压力和效果..诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以性玩具为目的..在黑市里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不真成了色狼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了达到触摸的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须把对像分身的资料传送到自身体内的纳米机器？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？资料的传送？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明没做过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有话对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先坐下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 克雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:16:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们彼此不需要互相隐瞒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么烦恼请告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈会一起帮你想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这阵子感觉..好像有点不像原来的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽去些什么可疑的地方 还有..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把女孩子们带回家之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的啦 芙琉妮是..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈是站在信任你的立场上才让你自个有一个家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们希望你自己也要有相应的自觉啊 克雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的这么在意我到底在做些什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里一起生活不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不就束缚到彼此的自由了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为我们对对方有着充分的了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能在彼此间保持着自由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是所谓的家族吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家子被束缚在一个屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是彼此间没有信任的证明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是克雷恩把奈纱叫出来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以克雷恩的地方就是奈纱的家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且爸爸妈妈就是因为关心你才用分身来这里..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说着这种的漂亮话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实只是想要一切按自己的意思来办而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷恩 你果然怪怪的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明不是这种会顶撞爸爸的孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷恩！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我想成那样 该不是爸妈的分身故障了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这一整天..好像跑个没完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么要冒出来..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样一直奔跑..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像就有什么东西要从嘴里冒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成了孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对父母的那一出完全是我乱发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 我也是一样..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.22,0:18:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为嫌麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为自己的步调被打乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把奈纱..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八点的祈祷时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:55.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从您的所在地指向寺院的方位是右前方约20度..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么祈祷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是要下载我的资料而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:18:59.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 一起祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要给白昼之星许愿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见芙琉妮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟奈纱道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我自己也不太明白 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 讨厌一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈纱的笑容..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷恩 我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但不可怕..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷恩好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话是我说才对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要搞得这么“显而易见”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三个家伙..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 有宝物 克雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上当了吧 两个蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种状况 还能讲成上当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摆了一道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收吧 小的们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收是啥意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
